{% extends '::base.html.twig' %}
{# INDIVIDUALAUS MAÄŒO INFO #}

{% block content %}

{% for flash_message in app.session.flashbag.get('success') %}
    <div style="color: #3fad46; font-size: 20px;">
        {{ flash_message }}
    </div>
{% endfor %}

{% for flash_message in app.session.flashbag.get('error') %}
    <div style="color: #ed0600; font-size: 20px;">
        {{ flash_message }}
    </div>
{% endfor %}

{{ dump(match) }}
Cia rodomas macas rastas pagal nurodyta ID. Jei maco neras, gausim 404 Not Found. <br>
Visa maco informacija pasiekiama per `match` kintamaji.<br><br>

{% if app.user == match.owner %}
    Linkas matomas tik maco kurejui <br>
    <a href="{{ path('basket_planner_match_edit', {'id' : match.id}) }}">Redaguoti maco aprasyma</a>
{% endif %}

<br><br>
Visi maco zaidejai: <br>
{% for player in match.players %}
    <li>{{ player.fullName }}</li>
{% endfor %}
<br><br>

Visos maco zinutes: <br>
{% if match.comments is not empty %}
    {% for comment in match.comments %}
        <li><strong>Zinute:</strong> {{ comment.message }}, <strong>Autorius:</strong> {{ comment.user.fullName }}</li>
    {% endfor %}
{% else %}
    Niekas nieko neparase... :(
{% endif %}

<br><br>

<div id="komentaru-forma">
    {{ render(controller('BasketPlannerMatchBundle:Comment:create', { 'id': match.id } )) }}
</div>

{% endblock %}